Title: Travelling through the body
DateModified: '2019-03-04'
DatePublished: '2019-03-04'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/travelling-through-the-body
SetInCountry: Argentina
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Gal Sanhueza
AuthorCountry: Argentina
Text: Since I've been in contact with performance art all my writing has a connection
  with my body. How experiences affect it and how sensations settle along time past.
  In connection with poetry travelling is still in the wishes list. Unfortunately,
  sometimes makes ends meet is difficult in a body that go against genres rules, especially
  in our country. I expect to connect travelling experience with art. Like a dayri
  I write down all the felling and sensations that arouse of being in touch with people
  and the community itself. I also take analog photographs to have a more descriptive
  picture of the places I visit. The body is our connection with the world that sorround
  us and I would like to put enphasis in it.
